ed="T" n="0747c09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0747c09"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011473">杭州龍興寺</placeName><persName key="A009897">可周</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0747c10"/><persName key="A009897">釋可周</persName>，俗姓傅，<placeName key="PL000000009723">晉陵</placeName>人也。出家于本部<placeName key="PL000000009713">建元<lb
ed="T" n="0747c11"/>寺</placeName>。循良厥性，切問于勤<ptr type="glossary" target="#g490"/>。友生<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1076"/>勉之曰：「非其<lb
ed="T" n="0747c12"/>地，樹之不生。今<placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>經謂之江，論謂之海，<lb
ed="T" n="0747c13"/>胡不往請業乎？」<persName key="A009897">周</persName>感其開導，挈囊達<ref type="place" target="#PL000000018603">彼</ref>，<lb
ed="T" n="0747c14"/>遇<persName key="A009898">雲表<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>盛集，窮《法華》<ref target="#A001019" type="person">慈恩</ref>大疏<ptr target="#n1077"/>，日就月<lb
ed="T" n="0747c15"/>將，斡運深趣<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g428"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0888-04-24" key="j20455102047009" notAfter-iso="+0892-06-01">昭宗初</date>，自<placeName key="PL000000018627">江西</placeName>迴<placeName key="PL000000014901">台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>之間，<lb
ed="T" n="0747c16"/>命其啟發。<date from-iso="+0912-01-27" key="j20541872054570" to-iso="+0913-02-13">梁<name>乾化</name>二年</date>，受<placeName key="PL000000011473">杭州龍興寺</placeName>召開<lb
ed="T" n="0747c17"/>演，黑、白眾恒有半千。<persName key="A003552"><roleName>兩浙武肅王</roleName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>命<lb
ed="T" n="0747c18"/>於<placeName key="PL000000011678">天寶堂</placeName>夜為冥司講經，鬼神現形扈衛，<lb
ed="T" n="0747c19"/>往往人覩焉。甞有祭銅官祠神，巫氏久請<lb
ed="T" n="0747c20"/>不下，後附巫曰：「吾隨從大神去<placeName key="PL000000011678">西關天寶<lb
ed="T" n="0747c21"/>堂</placeName>聽法方迴。」<persName key="A003552">武肅王</persName>聞而鄭重，賚<persName key="A009897">周</persName>中金<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1078"/><lb
ed="T" n="0747c22"/>如意并鉢、紫衣一副，加號<persName key="A009897">精志通明</persName>焉。以<lb
ed="T" n="0747c23"/><date from-iso="+0926-06-16" key="j20594412059679" to-iso="+0927-02-09"><name>天成</name>元年</date>，終于<placeName key="PL000000011474">觀音院</placeName>本房。初，<persName key="A009897">周</persName><date from-iso="+0897-02-10" key="j20487242049077" to-iso="+0898-01-29"><name>乾寧</name>四年</date><lb
ed="T" n="0747c24"/>戾止<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1057"/><placeName key="PL000000014841">台州松山寺</placeName>講疏，闕鈔，遂依疏節成<lb
ed="T" n="0747c25"/>五卷，曰《評經鈔》，《音訓》五帖，解<persName key="A001519">宣律師</persName>《法華序<lb
ed="T" n="0747c26"/>鈔》一卷，行于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000011308 #PL000000008363">浙之左右</ref>。弟子相繼不絕。</p>
